H0.text: Which group had a number one hit in 2009 with 'I Gotta Feeling'. The Black Eyed Peas

H1.text: Which group had a number one hit in 2009 with 'I Gotta Feeling'. Lady Gaga

H2.text: Which group had a number one hit in 2009 with 'I Gotta Feeling'. Kanye West

H3.text: Which group had a number one hit in 2009 with 'I Gotta Feeling'. TBEP

A4.text: I Gotta Feeling is a song by American group the Black Eyed Peas from their fifth studio album The E.N.D. (2009).

A5.text: It was written and composed by all the members of the Black Eyed Peas (credited as William Adams, Allan Pineda, Jaime Gomez, and Stacy Ferguson) together with French producers David Guetta and Frédéric Riesterer.
